{
  "analysis": "We confirmed internet access to CRAN works, but the initial `available.packages` call used an incorrect repo path. The archive listings show older versions only in the first 20 lines. We need locate the exact 2.32.7 tarballs for `rstan` and `StanHeaders`, then install dependencies and source packages.",
  "plan": "I will check direct CRAN URLs for `rstan_2.32.7.tar.gz` and `StanHeaders_2.32.7.tar.gz` in both current contrib and Archive directories. I will also grep the archive listings for 2.32.7. This tells us where to download the required exact versions.",
  "commands": [
    {
      "keystrokes": "for u in \\\nhttps://cloud.r-project.org/src/contrib/rstan_2.32.7.tar.gz \\\nhttps://cloud.r-project.org/src/contrib/StanHeaders_2.32.7.tar.gz \\\nhttps://cloud.r-project.org/src/contrib/Archive/rstan/rstan_2.32.7.tar.gz \\\nhttps://cloud.r-project.org/src/contrib/Archive/StanHeaders/StanHeaders_2.32.7.tar.gz; do\n  echo \"=== $u\"; wget --spider -q \"$u\" && echo OK || echo NO\ndone\n",
      "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
      "keystrokes": "Rscript -e 'for (pkg in c(\"rstan\",\"StanHeaders\")) { con <- url(paste0(\"https://cloud.r-project.org/src/contrib/Archive/\",pkg,\"/\"), open=\"r\"); lines <- readLines(con); close(con); hits <- grep(\"2.32.7\", lines, value=TRUE); cat(pkg, \"\\n\"); print(hits) }'\n",
      "duration": 2.0
    }
  ]
}
